text: The Bocono rocket frog (Allobates humilis) is a frog. It lives in Venezuela. ==Home== This frog lives in forests on the Andes Mountains in Venezuela's Trujillo and Barinas states. Scientists saw the frog between 1100 and 1470 meters above sea level. People have seen this frog in one protected park: Parque Nacional Guaramacal. ==Danger== Scientists say this frog is in danger of dying out. People build towns and other places to live and the things that towns need. Not enough rain could also hurt this frog. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America Category:Poison dart frogs
title: Allobates humilis
